We brought back `<Routes/>`.

``` js
// 0.4.x
var routes = (
  <Route handler={App} location="history">
    <Route name="about" handler="about"/>
  </Route>
);

// 0.5.x
var routes = (
  <Routes location="history">
    <Route handler={App}>
      <Route name="about" handler="about"/>
    </Route>
  </Routes>
);
```

## Changes
